# Custom Prompt Prefix Demo
# Shows how to customize the prompt with ANSI colors

Output examples/dvds/custom-prompt.svg

Set Width 800
Set Height 400
Set FontSize 16
Set Title "Custom Prompt Demo"
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[36m➜\x1b[0m "

Type "echo 'Custom cyan arrow prompt!'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
